ActHistoric Sites and Monuments Act
PrecisAppointment of TIMOTHY J. CHRISTIAN, Q.C., of North Saanich, British Columbia, to be a member of the Historic Sites and Monuments Board of Canada, as a representative of the Province of British Columbia, to hold office during pleasure for a period of five years, effective May 19, 2018.
